Microservices Architecture:
===========================

    - App should be easy to deploy
    - Scale up and down based on traffic
    - free from all technological dependencies


    Objectives:
    ===========

        - What is Microservices>
        - Microservices Architecture
        - Advantages & Disadvantages
        - Microservices vs Monolithic
        - Runtime Environment

    Microservices:
    --------------

        - Creating smaller APIs to handle a very specific concern.
        
    Characteristics:
    ----------------

        - Autonomous 
        - Specialized

    Advantages:
    -----------

        - Flexible Scaling
        - Easy Deployment
        - Technological Freedom
        - Reusable code
        - Resilience

    Disadvantages:
    --------------

        - Spawning
        - Maintenance

    